(2957, 'content', '<p><span style="font-family:SimSun;"></span><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128104559_26658.jpg" alt="" /> </p><p><br /></p><p><span style="line-height:1.5;"> </span> </p><h2><span style="color:#337FE5;">健康禮遇奢華，定位優質生活方式</span> </h2><p><span style="line-height:1.5;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128110713_68335.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="line-height:1.5;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128110729_97821.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="line-height:1.5;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128110821_65080.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="line-height:1.5;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128111201_32897.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="line-height:1.5;"> </span> </p><p><span style="font-size:18px;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';color:#337FE5;"><strong>但物質的富足遠不如身體健康來的珍貴...</strong></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:18px;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';color:#337FE5;"><strong><br /></strong></span> </p><p><br /></p><p><span style="font-size:18px;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';color:#337FE5;"><strong> </strong></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">但主觀意願的美好有時卻抵不過客觀事態的嚴重。眾所周知，在中華大地，尤其是經濟發達的</span><span style="font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">一線城市， “藍天白雲” 竟成為稀缺資源。長期受到霧霾和沙塵暴的侵襲，對居民健康構</span><span style="font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">成嚴重威脅，健康指數有所下降，重創對“健康奢華”的高品質生活的追求。</span> </p><p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128111849_82719.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:SimSun;"><br /></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128112245_85026.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:SimSun;"> </span> </p><p><span style="font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">世界衛生組織在2005年版《空氣質量準則》 中指出：當PM2.5年均濃度達</span><span style="line-height:1.5;"><span style="font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">到每立方米</span><span style="color:#E53333;font-size:18px;"><span style="font-family:SimSun;">35</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;">微克</span></span><span style="font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">時，人的死亡風險比每立方米10微克的情形約</span><span style="color:#E53333;font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">增加15%</span><span style="font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">。</span></span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">我國南開大學國家環境保護城市空氣顆粒物污染防治重點實驗室、中國環</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">境科學研究院大氣環境研究所專家發布的論文也稱，“PM2.5濃度每升高</span><span style="line-height:1.5;"><span style="color:#E53333;font-size:18px;"><span style="font-family:SimSun;">10</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;">微克</span></span><span style="font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">/立方米，我國居民每日</span><span style="color:#E53333;font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">死亡率上升0.31%</span><span style="font-size:18px;">。</span></span> </p><br /><p><br /></p><p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128112409_67419.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128112955_75317.png" alt="" /> </p><p><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128113043_70867.png" alt="" /> </p><p><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128113232_43524.png" alt="" /> </p><p><br /></p><p><span style="font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;">在中國，癌細胞最頻繁“光顧”的人體</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;">組織，可以說，這十種腫瘤佔據了所有</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;">腫瘤類型的80%以上。</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;">由於一些特殊原因，中國一些城市表現</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;">出了“地方特色”。比如北京、上海等</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;">大城市，女性乳腺癌的發病率已超過了</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;">肺癌，名列第一；而廣東則是鼻咽癌高</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;">發地； 江蘇啟東是肝癌的高發地； 河南</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;">林縣食管癌病人之多讓人側目。</span> </p><p><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128113450_28539.png" alt="" /> </p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><h3><span style="font-family:SimHei;font-size:24px;color:#337FE5;">價格不菲的血管成形術</span> </h3><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';font-size:18px;color:#337FE5;"> </span> </p><p><span style="color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">冠狀動脈球囊成形術（ Angioplasty）， 专</span><span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">治心肌梗塞、心脏病、冠心病.就是醫生以</span><span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">一根特殊設計的心導管，放進病人心臟血</span><span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">管狹窄的部位，然后替導管末端的氣球充</span><span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">氣。當氣球脹起，便把造成血管狹管的斑</span><span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">塊擠開，血流回復暢順，減少病人因心肌</span><span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">缺血缺氧而出現心絞痛的情況。</span> </p><p><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128113809_50577.png" alt="" /> </p><p><span style="color:#000000;font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;">為了減少血管可能會再次塌下的機會，一般來</span><span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;">說，都會在血管植入支架。支架的作用是撐着</span><span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;">張開了的血管，減少它的塌陷。隨著科技的發</span><span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;">展，支架的類型和效能亦有所提升。</span> </p><p><br /></p><p><span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128113923_65633.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><br /></p><p><span style="color:#000000;font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;">現時常用的支架有三種，包括裸金屬、</span><span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;">藥物塗層、生物工程支架和最新的雙療</span><span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;">法支架 。</span><span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;">舊式支架需要每五年重新做手術替換，</span><span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;">最新科技已可使用終身。</span> </p><p><span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128114142_46161.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><br /></p><h3>癌症 – &nbsp;耗資龐大的標靶治療</h3><p><span style="font-family:SimSun;color:#000000;font-size:16px;">在癌症的非手術治療中，電療及化療</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimSun;color:#000000;font-size:16px;">最常採用。但近年開始使用標靶治療</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimSun;color:#000000;font-size:16px;">這種較為嶄新的抗癌方法。</span> </p><p><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimHei;color:#E53333;font-size:32px;"><strong>但是......</strong></span> </p><p><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimHei;color:#E53333;font-size:32px;"><strong> </strong></span> </p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;">標靶治療的費用往往是很高昂的！</span></strong> </p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128114735_92136.png" alt="" /><br /></span></strong> </p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;"><br /></span></strong> </p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128133107_62374.jpg" alt="" /><br /></span></strong> </p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;"><br /></span></strong> </p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141205/20141205151646_49374.png" alt="" /><br /></span></strong> </p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;"> </span></strong> </p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;">醫療保障的主要目標是合理組織財政資源，滿足與經濟發展水平相適應的醫療資金需求，簡言之，就是</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;">“有錢看病”。 “有錢看病”，看似簡單的問題卻是公認的“世界難題”。現存的社會醫療保險覆蓋範</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;">圍狹窄、改革不配套、政府投入不足等問題，導致醫藥費用不斷上漲，而醫藥補貼未見增加。面對此種</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;">情況，正為多元化醫療保障謀得發展空間。 「醫世無憂」 ——財富增值計劃為您合理建立您的財富與</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;">健康坐標，打造“一世無憂”生活模式。</span> </p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128133424_44616.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128133522_51584.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128133618_36931.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128133648_21079.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128133715_94586.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128133746_42576.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128133813_17380.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128133842_22409.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128133914_90507.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128133943_97059.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128134955_25581.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128135059_88557.png" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;"><br /></span> </p><p><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:SimSun;"> </span> </p><h3><span style="color:#337FE5;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong>支付醫療開支</strong></span> </h3><p><span style="color:#337FE5;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128135239_24517.png" alt="" /><br /></strong></span> </p><p><span style="color:#337FE5;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128135332_40467.png" alt="" /><br /></strong></span> </p><p><span style="color:#337FE5;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128135452_93236.png" alt="" /><br /></strong></span> </p><p><span style="color:#337FE5;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128135544_47729.png" alt="" /><br /></strong></span> </p><p><span style="color:#337FE5;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong> </strong></span> </p><p><strong><span style="font-size:12px;color:#000000;">* 註有「 *」之「保障／最高限額」表示在提交予本公司作賠償申請的正式賬單或收據上所示之每項分類費用須符合合理及慣常費用之規定。</span> </strong> </p><strong><br /></strong> <p><br /></p><p><span style="color:#337FE5;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128135724_29864.jpg" alt="" /><br /></strong></span> </p><p><span style="color:#337FE5;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128135836_21160.png" alt="" /><br /></strong></span> </p><p><span style="color:#337FE5;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128135900_21350.png" alt="" /><br /></strong></span> </p><p><span style="color:#337FE5;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong><br /></strong></span> </p><p><span style="color:#337FE5;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128135951_16381.png" alt="" /><br /></strong></span> </p><p><span style="color:#337FE5;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128140015_47824.png" alt="" /><br /></strong></span> </p><p><span style="color:#337FE5;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong><br /></strong></span> </p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><span style="color:#337FE5;line-height:1.5;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128142317_91845.jpg" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><span style="color:#337FE5;line-height:1.5;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"> </span> </p><p><span style="font-family:SimSun;color:#000000;font-size:18px;">• 每次旅程可享US$125,000限額之以下服務：</span> </p><p><span style="font-family:SimSun;color:#000000;font-size:18px;">– (a) 緊急醫療運送</span> </p><p><span style="font-family:SimSun;color:#000000;font-size:18px;">• 會根據受保人狀況的嚴重程度，安排以飛機、陸地或空中救護交通工具、</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;font-size:18px;">火車或其他適當及可使用的方法運送受保人。</span> </p><p><span style="font-family:SimSun;color:#000000;font-size:18px;">– (b) 運返遺體</span> </p><p><span style="font-family:SimSun;color:#000000;font-size:18px;">– (c) 安排家屬探訪</span> </p><p><span style="font-family:SimSun;color:#000000;font-size:18px;">• 旅程期間身故或因於旅程期間開始的嚴重受傷或疾病而住院持續超過五(5)日，而當時受</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;font-size:18px;">保人並無成人直系親屬成員陪伴在側本公司將會安排一(1)名成人直系親屬成員前往受保</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;font-size:18px;">人身故或住院的地點以便照顧受保人，以及支付該名成人直系親屬成員是次的旅程費用</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;font-size:18px;">(來回旅費及酒店住宿)。</span> </p><p><span style="font-family:SimSun;color:#000000;font-size:18px;">– (d) 送返未成年兒童</span> </p><p><span style="font-family:SimSun;color:#000000;font-size:18px;">• 受保人獨自與未成年兒童外遊之旅程是在遞派至尊明珠醫療2（即香港或澳門，視</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;font-size:18px;">屬何情況而定）以外的國家或地方而受保人在該旅程期間身故或因於旅程期間開始</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;font-size:18px;">的嚴重受傷或疾病而住院持續超過五(5)日，本公司將會安排一(1)名成人直系親屬成</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;font-size:18px;">員前往受保人身故或住院的地點以便照顧該未成年兒童，及陪伴最多兩(2)名未成年</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;line-height:1.5;font-size:18px;">兒童返回其正常居住地點，並支付有關的旅程費用(來回旅費及酒店住宿)</span> </p><p><span style="font-family:SimSun;color:#000000;font-size:18px;">– 24 小時全球電話諮詢服務</span> </p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><span style="line-height:1.5;"> </span> </p><h3><span style="color:#337FE5;font-size:24px;">中國境內醫院直付服務</span> </h3><p><span style="font-family:SimSun;font-size:18px;">步骤一：致电保險公司预先入院登记查询国内客户免费热线400XXXXXXX，或国内客户身处香港时热线</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimSun;font-size:18px;">2XXX XXXX，查询详情及索取申请表格</span> </p><p><span style="font-family:SimSun;font-size:18px;">步驟二：</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimSun;font-size:18px;">填妥入院前登记表格并于入院前最少五个工作天交回给我们</span> </p><p><span style="font-family:SimSun;font-size:18px;">步驟三：</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimSun;font-size:18px;">保險公司会向有关入住医院发出「住院付款保证信」</span> </p><p><span style="font-family:SimSun;font-size:18px;">步驟四:</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimSun;font-size:18px;">入院时，请向医院提交受保人之身份证明文件以作核实</span> </p><p><span style="font-family:SimSun;font-size:18px;">步驟五:</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimSun;font-size:18px;">出院后，医院会将单据直接递交给我们, 理赔完成后，如有差额情况出现，保險公司将专函保</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-family:SimSun;font-size:18px;">单持有人，按入院前登记表格所注之条款及细则，于发信日十四天后直接从银联卡中扣除。</span> </p><p><span style="font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">註一：入院前需授權保險公司從銀聯卡帳戶收取差額</span> </p><p><span style="font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">註二： 入住医院挂帐服务可以安排在中华人民共和国境内之指定145间医院，</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:18px;font-family:SimSun;">医院名单请向我司查詢</span> </p><p><span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;"><br /></span> </p><p><span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;"> </span> </p><h3><span style="color:#337FE5;font-family:SimHei;font-size:24px;">香港私家醫院直付服務</span> </h3><p><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128142952_32356.png" alt="" /> </p><p><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128143026_29401.png" alt="" /> </p><p><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128143052_51062.png" alt="" /> </p><p><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128143120_52987.png" alt="" /> </p><p><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128143153_80120.png" alt="" /> </p><p><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128143257_31820.png" alt="" /> </p><p><br /></p><p>註：可安排所有香港的私家醫院標準私家單人病房</p><p><br /></p><p><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128143345_98230.jpg" alt="" /> </p><p><br /></p><p><span style="font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;color:#000000;"><img src="http://hs-album.oss.aliyuncs.com/static/87/f7/a7/image/20141128/20141128143837_26516.jpg" alt="" /><br /></span> </p><p><br /></p>'),
